      "rationale": "The Navier-Stokes solver was verified against the lid-driven cavity benchmark (Re = 1000) and a rotating disk flow analytical solution. Errors in velocity components were below 0.5% relative to reference solutions, confirming correct numerical implementation."
    },
    {
