    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1.0 across all COU operating conditions. The assessment team acknowledges that the boundary condition dataset used for model inputs predates the February 2026 model revision; re-validation against updated inputs is planned but does not preclude acceptance at this stage given the marginal nature of the revision and the conservative safety margins demonstrated.",
